    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146310/extras/63285971aa5fd507ea281539a639e14c.poster.avif?t=1772138856\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146310/extras/63285971aa5fd507ea281539a639e14c.webm?t=1772138856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146310/extras/63285971aa5fd507ea281539a639e14c.mp4?t=1772138856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >King of the Hill</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Battle it out in chaotic arenas where only one can hold the cup. Stay on top to score—but everyone else is coming for your throne, and they’ll do whatever it takes to knock you down.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146310/extras/5c1d439c34cfe05b093053e718456efc.poster.avif?t=1772138856\" width=800 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146310/extras/5c1d439c34cfe05b093053e718456efc.webm?t=1772138856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146310/extras/5c1d439c34cfe05b093053e718456efc.mp4?t=1772138856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146310/extras/23c2e75721157474ab41309485101cc5.poster.avif?t=1772138856\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146310/extras/23c2e75721157474ab41309485101cc5.webm?t=1772138856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146310/extras/23c2e75721157474ab41309485101cc5.mp4?t=1772138856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play with your friends</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump into the madness with your crew or go full free-for-all. Team up, betray, laugh, scream—every match becomes personal when your friends are in the arena. And if you’re looking for new rivals (or allies), our Discord community is super welcoming and always ready to rumble with new players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146310/extras/5c1d439c34cfe05b093053e718456efc.poster.avif?t=1772138856\" width=800 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146310/extras/5c1d439c34cfe05b093053e718456efc.webm?t=1772138856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146310/extras/5c1d439c34cfe05b093053e718456efc.mp4?t=1772138856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146310/extras/2dbbe29629910b9cdeda22c10ce3711a.poster.avif?t=1772138856\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146310/extras/2dbbe29629910b9cdeda22c10ce3711a.webm?t=1772138856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146310/extras/2dbbe29629910b9cdeda22c10ce3711a.mp4?t=1772138856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Customize your champion</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Style your fighter with wild outfits, spooky masks, and absurd skins. Intimidate, distract, or just look ridiculous while you rumble. Victory is great—dripping in soul-powered fashion is better.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146310/extras/5c1d439c34cfe05b093053e718456efc.poster.avif?t=1772138856\" width=800 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146310/extras/5c1d439c34cfe05b093053e718456efc.webm?t=1772138856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146310/extras/5c1d439c34cfe05b093053e718456efc.mp4?t=1772138856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146310/extras/8499b6613b364913a9ee64e76109bdfe.poster.avif?t=1772138856\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146310/extras/8499b6613b364913a9ee64e76109bdfe.webm?t=1772138856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146310/extras/8499b6613b364913a9ee64e76109bdfe.mp4?t=1772138856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146310/extras/81f5de2af292c29560f7e15c49a4a2fe.poster.avif?t=1772138856\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146310/extras/81f5de2af292c29560f7e15c49a4a2fe.webm?t=1772138856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146310/extras/81f5de2af292c29560f7e15c49a4a2fe.mp4?t=1772138856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose your artifact</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Before each match, pick two powerful artifacts to bring into battle. Once you're in, collect enough souls to activate them—then unleash chaos by freezing your rivals, knocking them off the map, or turning invisible to strike when they least expect it. Use them wisely… or combine them for the ultimate power move.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146310/extras/5c1d439c34cfe05b093053e718456efc.poster.avif?t=1772138856\" width=800 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146310/extras/5c1d439c34cfe05b093053e718456efc.webm?t=1772138856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146310/extras/5c1d439c34cfe05b093053e718456efc.mp4?t=1772138856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146310/extras/c26324cf37867f77eee6f9796f0e0fd0.poster.avif?t=1772138856\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146310/extras/c26324cf37867f77eee6f9796f0e0fd0.webm?t=1772138856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146310/extras/c26324cf37867f77eee6f9796f0e0fd0.mp4?t=1772138856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Collect Souls </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Souls fuel your strategy. Gather them throughout the match to activate your artifacts and gain the upper hand. Every soul brings you one step closer to total chaos</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br> <br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146310/extras/5c1d439c34cfe05b093053e718456efc.poster.avif?t=1772138856\" width=800 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146310/extras/5c1d439c34cfe05b093053e718456efc.webm?t=1772138856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146310/extras/5c1d439c34cfe05b093053e718456efc.mp4?t=1772138856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146310/extras/ba56302291a7390f9d6f1597b0eb348e.poster.avif?t=1772138856\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146310/extras/ba56302291a7390f9d6f1597b0eb348e.webm?t=1772138856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146310/extras/ba56302291a7390f9d6f1597b0eb348e.mp4?t=1772138856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Reach to the Top</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Climbing is only half the battle. Bounce, dash, and punch your way up while dodging traps—and the fists of every other contender fighting for control.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146310/extras/5c1d439c34cfe05b093053e718456efc.poster.avif?t=1772138856\" width=800 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146310/extras/5c1d439c34cfe05b093053e718456efc.webm?t=1772138856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146310/extras/5c1d439c34cfe05b093053e718456efc.mp4?t=1772138856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146310/extras/2652269478904f0867e66f1eaaba4ac4.poster.avif?t=1772138856\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146310/extras/2652269478904f0867e66f1eaaba4ac4.webm?t=1772138856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146310/extras/2652269478904f0867e66f1eaaba4ac4.mp4?t=1772138856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Don’t Fall</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Falling doesn’t kill you—but it costs you precious time. Every second counts in these intense 5–7 minute matches, and while you're scrambling to climb back up, others are racking up points. The top is a war zone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p>",
